commit.message:
varray.h (VARRAY_TOP_GENERIC_PTR): Remove spurious parameter.

	* varray.h (VARRAY_TOP_GENERIC_PTR): Remove spurious parameter.
	(VARRAY_TOP_CHAR_PTR): Likewise.
correct filenames for 2001-07-03  Stan Shebs  <shebs@apple.com>

From-SVN: r43768
